## 11 — ACCESSIBILITY (NON-NEGOTIABLE)

These are requirements, not suggestions. Every component ships with these or it ships broken.

**Keyboard:**
- All interactive elements reachable via `Tab`
- `focus-visible` ring on all interactive elements: `box-shadow: var(--shadow-focus)`; never `outline: none` without a replacement
- `Escape` closes modals, dropdowns, drawers
- Dialogs trap focus while open

**Semantics:**
- Page structure: `<header>`, `<main>`, `<nav>`, `<aside>`, `<footer>` — not all `<div>`
- Buttons: `<button>` — never `<div onClick>` or `<span onClick>`
- Navigation: `<nav>` with `aria-label` distinguishing multiple navs
- Lists: `<ul>`/`<ol>` for navigation and option groups
- Headings: one `<h1>` per page, logical hierarchy (no skipping levels)
- Images: `alt` text always (empty `alt=""` for decorative images)
- Icons without labels: `aria-label` on the button/link, `aria-hidden="true"` on the icon

**Form fields:**
- Every input paired with a `<label>` (visible or `sr-only`)
- Error messages linked via `aria-describedby`
- Required fields marked `aria-required="true"` AND visually (asterisk with legend)

**Color:**
- Text contrast ≥ 4.5:1 on background (all `--color-text-*` tokens already meet this)
- Never convey state (error, success) by color alone — always add icon or text

---

## 12 — DATA DISPLAY PATTERNS

### Stat card

```tsx
<div className="stat-card">
  <p className="stat-label">Total Revenue</p>
  <p className="stat-value">$48,295</p>
  <p className="stat-delta stat-delta--up">
    <TrendingUp size={12} /> +12.5% from last month
  </p>
</div>
```

```css
.stat-card   { background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: var(--space-6); }
.stat-label  { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-tertiary); font-weight: 500; }
.stat-value  { font-size: var(--text-2xl); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-primary); letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight); margin-top: var(--space-1); }
.stat-delta  { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-1); font-size: var(--text-xs); margin-top: var(--space-2); }
.stat-delta--up   { color: var(--color-success); }
.stat-delta--down { color: var(--color-error); }
```

### List item

```tsx
<div className="list-item">
  <div className="list-item-icon">{icon}</div>
  <div className="list-item-content">
    <p className="list-item-title">{title}</p>
    <p className="list-item-subtitle">{subtitle}</p>
  </div>
  <div className="list-item-trailing">{trailing}</div>
</div>
```

```css
.list-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-3); padding: var(--space-3) 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
.list-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.list-item-icon { flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--color-text-tertiary); }
.list-item-content { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
.list-item-title    { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 500; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
.list-item-subtitle { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-text-tertiary); margin-top: 2px; }
.list-item-trailing { flex-shrink: 0; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-secondary); }
```

