## 14 — CONSISTENCY CHECKLIST

Before marking any component or page done, verify every item:

**Visual:**
- [ ] All colors use design token variables — no hardcoded values
- [ ] All spacing uses `--space-*` tokens — no arbitrary pixel values
- [ ] All text uses `--text-*` scale tokens
- [ ] All border radii use `--radius-*` tokens
- [ ] Font is Geist/Inter — no system fonts

**States:**
- [ ] Hover state on all interactive elements
- [ ] Focus-visible ring on all focusable elements
- [ ] Active/pressed state on buttons
- [ ] Disabled state looks different, cursor is `not-allowed`
- [ ] Loading state prevents double-submission
- [ ] Error state is visible and descriptive
- [ ] Empty state is designed (not blank)

**Accessibility:**
- [ ] Every input has a label
- [ ] Every icon-only button has `aria-label`
- [ ] Heading hierarchy is logical (h1 → h2 → h3)
- [ ] Color contrast passes (no custom lighter text colors)

**Motion:**
- [ ] Content entering viewport fades + slides up
- [ ] No abrupt visibility changes (no instant `display: none` toggle)
- [ ] `prefers-reduced-motion` media query in global CSS

**Consistency:**
- [ ] This component uses the same card/button/input style as every other page
- [ ] Icon sizes match the surrounding context
- [ ] Layout spacing is consistent with sibling pages

