## 15 — ANTI-PATTERNS: THE REJECT LIST

Immediately refactor any code containing these patterns:

| Anti-pattern | Correct pattern |
|---|---|
| Hardcoded `#hex` color | `var(--color-*)` token |
| `font-size: 14px` | `var(--text-sm)` |
| `padding: 18px 12px` | `var(--space-4) var(--space-3)` |
| `border-radius: 6px` | `var(--radius-md)` |
| `color: gray` | `var(--color-text-tertiary)` |
| `background: #fff` | `var(--color-bg)` |
| `<div onClick={…}>` | `<button type="button" onClick={…}>` |
| `outline: none` (no replacement) | `box-shadow: var(--shadow-focus)` |
| Spinner for content loading | Skeleton matching content layout |
| Blank div for empty state | Designed empty state with icon + copy + CTA |
| `display: none` toggle | Opacity/transform transition |
| `width`/`height` in transitions | `transform` + `opacity` only |
| `font-family: Arial` | `var(--font-sans)` |
| `font-weight: 700` in product UI | `font-weight: 600` (headings) or `500` (labels) |
| Center-aligned body text > 2 lines | Left-aligned |
| Multiple accent-colored buttons in one view | One `primary`, rest `secondary`/`ghost` |
| Mixing icon libraries | Lucide only |
| `style={{ color: 'red' }}` inline | CSS class with semantic token |

