## QUICK REFERENCE CARD

```
Backgrounds:    --color-bg  →  --color-surface  →  --color-surface-2  →  --color-surface-3
Text:           primary (headings) → secondary (body) → tertiary (captions)
Accent:         --color-accent — use sparingly, max 2-3 visible at once
Spacing grid:   4px base — always multiples of 4
Border radius:  sm(4) md(8) lg(12) xl(16) full(9999)
Type scale:     xs(11) sm(13) base(15) md(17) lg(20) xl(24) 2xl(30) 3xl(36)
Duration:       fast(150ms) normal(200ms) slow(300ms)
Easing:         entering=--ease-out  leaving=--ease-in  moving=--ease-in-out
Icons:          Lucide only, 1.5 stroke, currentColor
Font:           Geist (primary) → Inter (fallback)
```
